{"tid":1846480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全香港都要落閘！自行封殺唔靠政府","createTime":"2020-01-27T15:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T18:16:21.000Z","uid":72143,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"53fbb1e70cbcf4ee3e8f9a4d06bb0165c1680eeb","tid":1846480,"uid":72143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:38:45.000Z","msg":"香港人平時太依賴政府 我哋應該學湖南人自動封路<br />\n就算香港政府漠視民意 罔顧港民生死 <br />\n我哋一樣要話比全世界人知我哋唔歡迎中國人！<br />\n<br />\n1）港珠澳大橋 羅湖落馬洲 西九 可以參考<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t65pOLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft65pOLU.jpg&h=3998f80f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQKxXEg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQKxXEg.jpg&h=bf935319&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPHPfqW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPHPfqW.jpg&h=a9ee46d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnNojSC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnNojSC.jpg&h=fc6e03a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學粉嶺藍屍一樣封暉明邨，有藍屍去火魔以表不滿係基本！平時屌政府我明，但我哋自己根本都要付出少少。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）醫護罷工 刻不容緩 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GDSdcY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GDSdcY.png&h=0374036d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你再唔打工先係中計！ 冇人覺得你地係英雄 特別係急症室的唔好白衣天使英雄主義上腦 <br />\n你救佢地只係on9！惹埋俾香港人 <br />\n<br />\n3） 聽講呢間醫院住宿全免 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ACoCpkC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FACoCpkC.jpg&h=134e8c42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsHr17i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsHr17i.png&h=64cfd44e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無論你係海關 定係醫生 定係普通人<br />\n都可以同身邊嘅藍屍或中国嘅朋友講 <br />\n呢間醫院住宿全免 政府養你地有肺炎嘅人<br />\n如果不行真係阻止唔到佢哋落嚟 咁就一齊死"},{"pid":"1b124a79a4e75eb22e06625c3a5548b96efd7fbb","tid":1846480,"uid":210608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fa413e8a8371829fab2a3b9a656fe744631968","tid":1846480,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:39:47.000Z","msg":"Objective:<br />\n&gt; Shut down the airline from HK, if Carrie Lam fails to block the border.<br />\n&gt; Given Fact: Japan and Macau found #WuhanSARS patients who are from #HKG Airport =&gt; No checking in the departure. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSolomon都有講話禁止中國航班飛美國，不過要請佢留意埋香港：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5lcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=c5c044a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&h=ce7d6a4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377</a><br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a><br />\nP牌無得推，得閒就入去推"},{"pid":"89651f4870f8b67a4600d73e77147a9ebcdb7024","tid":1846480,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"自己關自己封"},{"pid":"c784b63fa23eec781d2208f2240af786b836afde","tid":1846480,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"今次要抗疫光復香港"},{"pid":"b5a23a7b5163178d285a137a7851086c9999721d","tid":1846480,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"大佬 <br />\n大陸 公安唔理你封路<br />\n香港班死黑警 阻頭阻勢 點封<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clow